#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfc:15 of
msgid ""
"`erfc` has experimental support for Python Array API Standard compatible "
"backends in addition to NumPy. Please consider testing these features by "
"setting an environment variable ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` and providing CuPy,"
" PyTorch, JAX, or Dask arrays as array arguments. The following "
"combinations of backend and device (or other capability) are supported."
msgstr ""
"`erfc` 除了支持 NumPy 外，还对 Python Array API 标准兼容的后端提供了"
"实验性支持。请考虑通过设置环境变量 ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` 并提供 CuPy、"
"PyTorch、JAX 或 Dask 数组作为参数来测试这些功能。以下后端与设备（或其他"
"能力）的组合是支持的。"

